property right of protection?

00:43:22.360 --> 00:43:25.690
And what is a state
owned enterprise?

00:43:25.690 --> 00:43:27.110
And so on and so forth.

00:43:27.110 --> 00:43:28.890
So it is complicated.

00:43:28.890 --> 00:43:30.380
And it is going to take time.

00:43:30.380 --> 00:43:34.790
