two presidents to move forward

00:43:34.790 --> 00:43:39.060
and to agree to discuss
those issues, I think,

00:43:39.060 --> 00:43:42.960
is compared with what we have
just gone through is progress.

00:43:42.960 --> 00:43:44.260
Yes.

