institutions because now they,

00:44:40.630 --> 00:44:46.180
in our daily political life,
are described or at least felt,

00:44:46.180 --> 00:44:49.990
perceived by some, to be
against U.S. interests.

00:44:49.990 --> 00:44:55.010
That is how some of the more
popular rhetoric has described

00:44:55.010 --> 00:44:57.630
institutions like yours.

00:44:57.630 --> 00:45:03.150
