You know, when I look back
and I consider the history

00:47:48.380 --> 00:47:53.720
of the United States role, it's
involvement, what has worked,

00:47:53.720 --> 00:47:56.230
how has it worked for
this country and others.

00:47:56.230 --> 00:48:01.050
That collaboration has
proven extremely efficient.

